name: ExtensionExplanationOfBenefit_SupportingInfo
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Element `ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo`, but has no comparisons.
